    "view": {
      "representation": "view",
      "value": "<p>To add a user attribute to an object, we add it via the Edit Parameter Interface.</p><p>Add a parameter to the User tab under either the Attributes or Primvars section in the RenderMan tab. The parameter must be located within the User folder and must be prefixed &quot;ri_user_&quot; to be read. </p><p>You must also supply a Tag Value to the parameter to inform Houdini and RenderMan of the type and allow interactive edits.</p><h2 id=\"UserAttributes-SettingupMatteIDasanExample\">Setting up MatteID as an Example</h2><p>Create a color attribute called &quot;ri_user_MatteID0&quot;. </p><p>The label is the UI displayed name.</p><p>Note we have used the tags field near the bottom, this is to inform Houdini and RenderMan of the RenderMan attribute. Valid types of values are listed below.</p><span class=\"confluence-embedded-file-wrapper image-center-wrapper confluence-embedded-manual-size\"><img class=\"confluence-embedded-image image-center\" width=\"598\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/thumbnails/544643715/rfh_addMatteUserAttr.png?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1754433118155&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2&amp;width=598&amp;height=421\" data-image-src=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/attachments/544643715/rfh_addMatteUserAttr.png?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1754433118155&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2\" data-height=\"786\" data-width=\"1115\" data-unresolved-comment-count=\"0\" data-linked-resource-id=\"544643733\" data-linked-resource-version=\"1\" data-linked-resource-type=\"attachment\" data-linked-resource-default-alias=\"rfh_addMatteUserAttr.png\" data-base-url=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki\" data-linked-resource-content-type=\"image/png\" data-linked-resource-container-id=\"544643715\" data-linked-resource-container-version=\"1\" data-media-id=\"83bb7290-93a7-40f3-ae66-d705d74733e7\" data-media-type=\"file\" srcset=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/thumbnails/544643715/rfh_addMatteUserAttr.png?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1754433118155&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2&amp;width=1115&amp;height=786 2x, https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/thumbnails/544643715/rfh_addMatteUserAttr.png?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1754433118155&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2&amp;width=598&amp;height=421 1x\"></span><p /><p>Valid Tag Values are listed here. These must match the expected data type of the Parameter chosen in the left hand pane called &quot;Create Parameters&quot;:</p><ul><li><p>int</p></li><li><p>float</p></li><li><p>color</p></li><li><p>point</p></li><li><p>vector</p></li><li><p>normal</p></li><li><p>hpoint</p></li><li><p>matrix</p></li><li><p>string</p></li></ul><p /><p>This will emit the following to the RIB.</p><div class=\"code panel pdl conf-macro output-block\" data-hasbody=\"true\" data-macro-id=\"c487bfed-0ac8-497e-8322-5adaa8f0b737\" data-macro-name=\"code\" style=\"border-width: 1px;\"><div class=\"codeContent panelContent pdl\">\n<pre class=\"syntaxhighlighter-pre\" data-syntaxhighlighter-params=\"brush: py; gutter: false; theme: Confluence\" data-theme=\"Confluence\"> Attribute &quot;user&quot; &quot;color MatteID0&quot; [0 1 0]</pre>\n</div></div><p />"
    }
  },
